      <title>欧盟国家猛烈抨击匈牙利反对乌克兰援助和入盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/eu-countries-slam-hungary-for-opposing-aid-accession-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国对匈牙利试图阻止向乌克兰提供资金并阻挠启动入盟谈判感到越来越沮丧，这有可能在其领导人会议上摊牌，就像美国对基辅的资金也存在疑问一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/eu-countries-slam-hungary-for-opposing-aid-accession-to-ukraine</guid>
